<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>E-realtor</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto:300,400,500,700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/mdb-ui-kit/6.4.1/mdb.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="/static/css/style.css"  rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<body>

    {{>navbar_logged data=data}}
    <div id="photo">
        <div id="searchbar">
            <input type="search" placeholder="Search..." autocomplete="off"><button><i
                    class="fa fa-search"></i></button>
        </div>
        <h1>Find the perfect home</h1>
        <p>for you and your family...</p>
        
    </div>

    <div id="para">
        Having a correct home is of paramount importance as it serves as the foundation of our daily lives. A home is not merely a physical structure but a sanctuary where we seek comfort, security, and a sense of belonging. It is a place where cherished memories are made, where we can unwind and recharge, and where our dreams take shape. Don't miss this rare opportunity to own a real gem that offers everything you've ever dreamed of in a home. Explore E-realtor now!  
    </div>
    <div id="options">
        <div class="image-box"><a href="/buy" id="buy"><img src="/static/images/buy.jpg" class="image" alt="buy">
            <h1 onmouseenter="opacity: 1">Buy</h1>
            <p>Looking for a comfortable place to call your home? Buy a property now. Get yourself a permanant home</p></a>
        </div>
        <div class="image-box"><a href="/sell" id="sell"><img src="/static/images/sell.jpg" class="image" alt="sell">
            <h1>Sell</h1>
            <p>Want to sell your house? Find intersted buyers easily who match your criteria here.</p></a>
        </div>
        <div class="image-box"><a href="/rent" id="rent"><img src="/static/images/rent.jpg" class="image" alt="room">
            <h1>Rent</h1>
            <p>Find a place to rent that checks all your boxes for comfy homes. Rent a place now!</p></a>
        </div>
    </div>

    {{>footer}}

</body>

</html>